import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' import styles from './StatusStatistics.module.css' export const StatusStatistics = () => { const statusCount = useSelector((state) => state.createTask.statusCount) return (
active {statusCount['active']}
ip {statusCount['inprogress']}
{' '} a {statusCount['urgent']}
{' '} a {statusCount['done']}
) }
